instanceVariables.TutorialText: Use WASD to move your character!
Use WASD to move your character!

Press 3 to summon your Arcane Hand.
Use it to click and move the crate!

Press 2 to summon your Arcane Shield.
Use it to block enemies and projectiles!

Use your Arcane Sword to break health packs!
Pick up green orbs to restore health!

Use your Arcane Sword to defeat slimes!
Beware your sword's brief cooldown!
Some doors require the use of a key!
Don't be afraid to use your shield, if overwhelmed by enemies
Touch the chest to finish the level!
